nabilien <is>gaṇa</is> {#cAdi#} zu <ls>P. 1,4,57</ls>\n), {#bravIhi#} (\n<ls>MBH. 3,10657.</ls> <ls n=\"MBH. 3,\">12470.</ls> <ls n=\"MBH. 3,\">13570.</ls> <ls n=\"MBH.\">4,321.</ls>\n<ls>MĀRK. P. 101,2</ls>), {#brUtAt#} (\n<ls>P. 7,1,35</ls>, <ab>Sch.</ab>),\n{#bra/vItu, brUta, bruvantu; abravam#} (<ab>ved.</ab> und\n<ls>MĀRK. P. 74,26.</ls> <ls n=\"MĀRK. P. 74,\">33</ls>), {#abruvam, abravIt (abravat#}\n<ls>MBH. 7,9283</ls> fehlerhaft für {#abravIt#}, wie die <ls>ed. Bomb.</ls> hat), {#bravIt#} (\n<ls>HARIV. 8214.</ls> <ls n=\"HARIV.\">8921</ls>), {#abrUtAm, abruvan (abrUvan#}\n<ls>MAITRYUP. 2,3</ls> wohl fehlerhaft), {#bra/vat#} <ab>ved.</ab>, {#bravATa#} (\n<ls>AV. 7,56,7</ls>); <ab>partic.</ab> {#bruva/nt, bra/vant#} (\n<ls>ṚV. 9,39,1</ls>); <ab>med.</ab> {#brUte, bruve, bruvImahi, brUmahe#} (\n<ls>BHĀG. P. 7,13,22</ls>), {#bruvate; bruvIta; brUzva, bruvaDvam#}\n(<ls>MBH. 3,2729</ls>, <ab>v. l.</ab>); {#abrUta#}; <ab>partic.</ab> {#bruvARa#} . Von allgemeinen Formen nur die 2te <ab>pl.</ab> <ab>prec.</ab> {#brUyAsta#} zu belegen\n<ls>N. 17,35</ls> (<ls>MBH. 3,2729</ls> statt dessen {#brUyAstat#}, die <ls>ed. Bomb.</ls> aber {#brUyAsta#} mit Erwähnung der Variante {#bruvaDvam#}) .", "equivalence_type": "explanatory", "source_type": "attested", "stratum": "", "differentia": "Вводный морфологический раздел: перечень форм и вариантов.", "review_status": "ai_translated", "reviewer": null, "provenance": {"model": "sonnet", "generator": "gen_opt_harness2.batched-masked", "schema_version": "pwg_ru.workflow_meta.v1", "root": "brU", "safe_root": "br_u", "rootmap_sha256": "e3a5775e275129b6472df8ac2edf0e3c1b82b0dbb1012403d9be4395e6160fdc", "input_raw_sha256": "bdaf9520d7fd2a15b55a7b8215e66054ef7db0c989206b2777a6c033beca2e54", "input_portrait_sha256": "13849fa65a3beb05e664208422578e2eeb96f6301a75e212a1ad18b0fe07448f", "generated_at": "2026-06-29T12:37:52Z", "wf_file": "wf_output.sc.brU.json", "promoted_by": "promote_final_cards.py"}}
